OL,3,CResident blames council inaction for
OL,4,Croad race crash
OL,6,F Watch Jonathan Brown's report on
OL,7,Fconcerns about driver safety in Swine,
OL,8,FEast Yorkshire.JA resident of a
OL,9,Fvillage which hosts an annual road
OL,10,Frace has blamed council inaction for a
OL,11,Fcrash which demolished a wall.JKarl
OL,12,FStephenson, of Swine, near Beverley,
OL,13,Fsaid the road used by the East Riding
OL,14,FStages Rally was flooded two days
OL,15,Fbefore Sunday's event.
OL,17,FBut he said it remained covered in mud
OL,18,Fand debris when the 120 cars raced
OL,19,Fthrough the village.
